        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>IRS Enhancement and Tax Gap Reduction Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill appropriates additional amounts to the Internal Revenue Service (IRS) in FY2021-FY2030 for tax enforcement, improving IRS technology infrastructure, and taxpayer services. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
